description.en: CATScoin is a cryptocurrency blockchain, with Proof of Stake (POS) and Masternode (MN) functions. Users can contribute to the network in two separate ways. Proof of Stake: 10% of every block reward goes to the stake holders of the project. Individuals that stake will receive a portion of the POS rewards. Masternodes: 90% of every bock reward goes to masternode holders.
